==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{rhymes|eɪʃǝn}}

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# {{economics}} A [[decrease]] in the general price level, that is, in the [[nominal]] [[cost]] of [[goods]] and [[services]] as well as [[wages]].
# {{rfv-sense}} {{economics}} A [[contraction]] in the [[volume]] of [[money]] and [[credit]] relative to available [[goods]].

